M'ara d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, ɣilen ad ṛuḥen ɣer leqsed nsen. M'ara heggin waḍu ɣer lebḥeṛ, a ten-id-yawi waḍu iwakken a ten-isɛeddin ɣer deffir.
Akken i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, ɣilen ad uɣalen d ireqqen m'ara walin lqaɛa.
